<body>  <section class="section green">
    <h2>🟩 What is Contact Gain?</h2>
    <p>Contact Gain is a smarter way to grow genuine, active WhatsApp contacts without relying on spammy promos or inactive link drops. It’s a system where one simple task earns access to a verified group of active people — no tricks, just real connection.</p>
  </section>  <section class="section blue">
    <h2>🟦 How It Started</h2>
    <p>It wasn’t always this easy. The system was born from frustration — after facing bans, limitations, and broken strategies that didn’t work. At a point, access to key platforms was lost, and everything seemed to fall apart. But instead of giving up, the experience was used to build something better.</p>
    <p>A platform that filters noise and rewards real effort. That’s how Contact Gain came to life.</p>
  </section>  <section class="section yellow">
    <h2>🟨 How It Works</h2>
    <p>Contact Gain runs on one simple idea: do one small task → get verified → gain access.</p>
    <p>Instead of joining endless promo groups with no engagement, each user completes a quick, easy task (like filling a form or sharing proof). Once verified, access is granted to a curated WhatsApp group filled with real, active contacts.</p>
    <p>This keeps the community valuable and spam-free.</p>
  </section>  <section class="section orange">
    <h2>🟧 Why It’s Better Than Regular Promo</h2>
